                <div class="pagetitle">Regional Booksellers Associations</div>
                
                
                  <div class="pagesubtitle">
                    Although the regional associations are not a part of the ABA, we do work quite    closely with them and encourage you to join them as well. The regional associations    provide a local focus, voice, and promotional and networking opportunities.
                  </div>
                
                <div class="doublegrayline">&nbsp;</div>
                
                  <div style="clear:both;">
                    
                    


<div class="commontext section" style="padding-bottom:10px;">
  
  
    <div class="sectionHeader">
      
          
            
            
          







<a href="/files/open/pdf/Regional_Guide.pdf">Regional Booksellers Association Guide</a>


        
    </div>
  
  <div style="vertical-align:top;">
    
      Here's an overview of the nine regional booksellers associations, their programs and services, and key information.
    
    
      <div style="padding-top:10px;">
        
          
          
          
        







<a href="/files/open/pdf/Regional_Guide.pdf">&gt;Download pdf guide.</a>


      </div>
    
  </div>
</div>

